evidence: "openMAXIMS - home of the openMAXIMS PAS/EPR" and description of a Patient Administration System and Electronic Patient Record indicate it is an end-user clinical application, not a library or infrastructure component.

"The latest generation of our full MAXIMS suite has become openMAXIMS, our first open source software product. It has the same rich functionality and currently includes: A full Patient Administration System... An Electronic Patient Record..." shows it is a general healthcare product, not research-specific tooling.
The presence of this README in a code repository for an open source product, with no mention of package managers or binaries, implies distribution primarily via the source repository.
